715439f-a.title: Manhattan: 126th Street (East) - 3rd Avenue
715439f-a.text:
167 East 126th Street, adjoining the N.W. corner of Third
Avenue. This is a two-story frame building.
1932.
J. Clarence Davies Collection, Museum of the City of New York.
Negative No. 52.
